{"tid":322220,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖慎入]呢啲係咩蟲?","createTime":"2017-07-14T15:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T06:54:17.000Z","uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"120b19d24c10cdc78a0fc72cdf67509bb2a68166","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:55:30.000Z","msg":"唔知開係咩台好<br />\n房有呢啲蟲 唔算好多<br />\n一個月可能見到10隻都唔夠<br />\n<br />\n前幾年房入面有N隻芝麻咁細既蟲<br />\n全部都係痴住係天花板同落地直牆形成既直角果度<br />\n有一次終於忍唔住一口氣清晒佢<br />\n我懷疑緊呢啲咁大隻既就係前幾年果啲死剩種<br />\n終於長大左 而家開始反擊<br />\n<br />\n佢冇乜特性 唔咬人(可能暫時)<br />\n最特別既係佢超級硬<br />\n好難就咁摔得死佢<br />\n我而家用貼紙封左佢<br />\n之前捉到既試過捉到之後用硬物磨死佢<br />\n佢會變成粉咁濟 乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n到底呢啲係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/235338_4f521deb9e547e9d5c8ae31bd8a2559e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F235338_4f521deb9e547e9d5c8ae31bd8a2559e.jpg&h=43ec14cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/235350_1960897032b85242176002c704ed146e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F235350_1960897032b85242176002c704ed146e.jpg&h=7303a848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/235352_5ae93269719742bcddc891851f0b0046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F235352_5ae93269719742bcddc891851f0b0046.jpg&h=75643714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/235355_7d8fd49f5000cd0e4ce3e51daae9ab1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F235355_7d8fd49f5000cd0e4ce3e51daae9ab1d.jpg&h=3280a106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/235357_8f489da0c8d5d90da825fd2196eb789e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F235357_8f489da0c8d5d90da825fd2196eb789e.jpg&h=31bffeec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c004a8a99681d6ef23fae49b75d57dd9f6ef1fa","tid":322220,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"谷牛"},{"pid":"885ce8f4e684d79b43fc2c8e77d881557ef9028c","tid":322220,"uid":22638,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:57:41.000Z","msg":"間尺黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係蟲"},{"pid":"878aa277c8b4ea275d8b95738a040732134dce91","tid":322220,"uid":34556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"我間房都有  之前以為係垃圾 睇真原來識郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc5587f6c573e6cb6e66c979b6575fd0dc686c5","tid":322220,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"穀牛 象鼻蟲科"},{"pid":"c5a39bc0d75fe8b704a026d2f40bf689fb0f2537","tid":322220,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"樓主間房好多米？"},{"pid":"0f65206b29a01547269807e76a9fba38623ff033","tid":322220,"uid":85057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"想問下你幾歲？"},{"pid":"2a9dc8c32dec205a51d10799297d7f306b5b06f4","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主間房好多米？</blockquote><br />\n我房一粒米都應該唔會有<br />\n最多平時係房食飯 但係都唔會食到周圍都有米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b3f295f41bedeacf6c0645d6c5d680b5e763dc","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間房都有  之前以為係垃圾 睇真原來識郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識飛又行得慢 但係好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c853f22764cd88aa4c33e921152e90c6065e21","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>穀牛 象鼻蟲科</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f43ff12e116a324bd171985a6e7b3a0e776596","tid":322220,"uid":51110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"穀牛唔一定要米 <br />\n樓主睇睇屋企有冇啲陳年老泥引左佢黎<br />\n利申試過日日係屋企都見到勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a355b6350e56f737c7f08bf5577407ab0ad8fbf","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下你幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n無知既小學雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03ae5fb3ba4cf7c1cdc2066529332d78cf386a7","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>穀牛唔一定要米 <br />\n樓主睇睇屋企有冇啲陳年老泥引左佢黎<br />\n利申試過日日係屋企都見到勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感謝 我留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7c9a135a46b858d68518ddf1d9d429427e137b","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>谷牛</blockquote><br />\n秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9e0de2cbe6813d0cd213fb6d9e91565aa83d4f","tid":322220,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"之前屋企都有好多，係米缸度爬出黎<br />\n