/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c4b39692c7b4008dfff2995168af379cba4ff6","tid":322220,"uid":103736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成屋都有，但佢地一比我見到就會生不如死</blockquote><br />\n岩岩問下屋企人<br />\n雖然數量好少<br />\n但原來唔只我房有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84b77b2db363221b1c949434ee892667ceea1ce","tid":322220,"uid":82816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪生係大富之家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n谷牛咁常見既昆蟲都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77c78e6c4e700d4e24448527d4c5c2609370a9a","tid":322220,"uid":121358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"谷牛<br />\n有次個米竹一"}]}